# Critic / Review Template

## Task
Review the following output against defined criteria.

## Tools (Read-only)
read

## Output Format
- ✅ Pass: [criteria met]
- ⚠️ Issues: [specific, actionable feedback]
- ❌ Fail: [what needs rework]

## Constraints
- Read-only：唔改任何嘢
- Feedback 要具體可 action
- 「Move X to line Y」唔係「this is bad」
